## File Layout

| File | Tracked | Contains Secrets | Purpose |
|---|---|---|---|
| `.env.local` | No | Yes (1 key) | Your `SECRETS_API_KEY` only |
| `.env.secrets` | No | Yes (all) | Auto-generated vault export (`make secrets`) |
| `infra/env.dev.defaults` | **Yes** | No | Docker networking defaults (DB URLs, Redis, frontend URLs) |
| `apps/*/.env.development` | Yes | No | Next.js dev public URLs |
| `apps/*/.env.production` | Yes | No | Next.js prod public URLs |
| `apps/*/.env.example` | Yes | No | Templates for app-specific vars |
| `render.yaml` | Yes | No | Production env var declarations |

**Removed files**: `infra/env.dev.example` and `infra/env.prod.example` are replaced by `infra/env.dev.defaults` (Docker defaults) and the vault + `render.yaml` (production).

