## Environment Matrix

Five layers must stay consistent. Use `make env-check` to validate deploy-facing envs. The **vault** is the credential source of truth.

| Layer | Role | How to Update |
|---|---|---|
| **Secrets Vault (Studio)** | Canonical store for all credentials | `POST /api/secrets` or `scripts/populate-vault.sh` |
| **Vercel Production** | App runtime env for Studio / apps | Vercel Dashboard / `vercel env add` |
| **Repo `.env.local`** | Local dev (holds `SECRETS_API_KEY` only) | Manual |
| **Hetzner .env** | Server + Docker (`/opt/paperwork-ops/.env`) | SSH + edit |
| **n8n container** | Inherits from Hetzner via `compose.yaml` | Map in `compose.yaml`, `docker compose restart n8n` |

